ISLAMABAD, Apr 21 (APP):Federal Minister for Maritime Affairs Syed Faisal gave media briefing to journalists after attending introductory meeting at Karachi Port Trust (KPT) , said a press release here  on Thursday.
The Minister attended to the question answer session of electronic and print media journalists and aptly responded to all the questions raised.
